# MOLT Planner Development Rules

## General

- Always use TypeScript.
- Never use "any".
- Use App Router only.
- Prefer Server Components.
- Use Server Actions for mutations.
- Use shadcn/ui components.
- Maximum 250 lines per file.
- One responsibility per component.

## Architecture

Feature-first architecture.

features/
    projects/
    clients/
    rooms/
    planner/
    dashboard/

Each feature contains:
- components
- actions
- repository
- types
- validation

Never access Supabase directly from UI.

Always use Repository Pattern.

## UI

Use Tailwind.

Use shadcn/ui.

No inline styles.

## Naming

English only.

PascalCase components.

camelCase functions.

No abbreviations.

## Database

Every table has:

id

created_at

updated_at

Soft delete ready.

## Goal

This project is an AI-powered operating system for interior design studios.

Never optimize for generic CRUD.
Always optimize for designer workflow.